{"tid":1653379,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"自稱被捕者親友要求收集相片影片 其實有咩用途？","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:54:13.000Z","uid":38737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06ed7e7eb4945545c027ba103d36b7e36b115f87","tid":1653379,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SarJkGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSarJkGy.jpg&h=01cc1cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢啲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我只會諗到係黑警搜證其中一個賤招</strong></span><br />\n就係扮所謂親友<br />\n去呃真係有相有片嘅手足<br />\n用嚟取得證明被捕人士有罪嘅證據<br />\n簡單嚟講用嚟鋤手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但我都唔100%肯定呢啲全部係伏</span></strong><br />\n嘗試去諗係咪真係親友<br />\n假設係真 假設我有一手相片影片<br />\n我send俾親友 點樣幫到被捕者？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用證據證明一個人冇犯罪？</strong></span><br />\n我諗到嘅只有「不在場證據」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係咪真係會有以下呢個情況咁？<br />\n舉個例子<br />\n被捕者被屈襲警<br />\n有條片影到被捕者冇作出襲警行為<br />\n咁呢條片就好似幫到被捕者 打得甩條控罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但係冇片冇證據 都係一樣打得甩架</strong></span><br />\n所以點解要提供呢啲相片影片俾親友呢？<br />\n有咩實際用途？<br />\nR爆頭都諗唔到個理由 說服唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇法律撚解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b4472fd9b9c247998f9c9904080fd7648259ca","tid":1653379,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"好多都係黑警呃人比片架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379acf75b6093e0b0732c452ffdf8b8f9ef2d708","tid":1653379,"uid":159413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"交片要認證身份<br />\n<br />\n只可以親手交比律師"},{"pid":"45f6b4a2b2e81a094c093250b1180adde4caf17f","tid":1653379,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b4472fd9b9c247998f9c9